==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''relativity'''

# the state of being [[relative]] to something else.
#{{physics}} the [[principle]] (due to [[Galileo]]) that the [[law]]s of [[physics]] should be the same for all [[observer]]s in [[uniform]] [[motion]].
#{{physics}} either of the two principles (due to [[Albert Einstein|Einstein]]) of [[special relativity]] or [[general relativity]].

